Ing '''buntuk lagari''' (''Pristis microdon''), a ausan dang ''largetooth sawfish'' ampong ''Leichhardt's sawfish'' king Ingles, metung yang [[:en:sawfish|sawfish]] ning [[:en:family (biology)|familia]] [[Pristidae]], a mayayakit king kadayatmalatan a [[:en:Indo-Pacific|Indo-West Pacific]] pilatan da reng [[:en:latitude|latitude]] a [[11th parallel north|11° N]] ampong [[39th parallel south|39° S]]. Kalupa de reng kayang kamaganak, uling pupunta ya murin king matabang a danum. Metung yang species o uring [[:en:critically endangered|misnang mamiligru]] (''critically endangered''), at miraras ya king kabang anggang {{convert|7|m|ft}}. King pamiparakal kayabe ya kareng [[ovoviviparous]].

